Download the loans by sector series

get_prestamos_osd.Rd

Download loans by sectors

Usage

get_prestamos_osd(osd = "consolidado")

Arguments

osd

string with the desired societies options: "consolidado", "bancos_multiples", "resto_osd".

Value

a tibble

Examples

get_prestamos_osd("consolidado")
